```{r bileducts 31818951, include=FALSE}

PMID_31818951 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('31818951', database = 'PubMed')

citation_31818951 <- paste0(PMID_31818951$journal,' ', PMID_31818951$year, ' ', PMID_31818951$month,';', PMID_31818951$volume,'(', PMID_31818951$number,'):', PMID_31818951$pages)

PubMed_31818951 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_31818951$eprint)

doi_31818951 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_31818951$doi)

Sys.sleep(2)

```
